# Vendored PUC-Rio Lua: the stock interpreter source and its official test
# suite are carried verbatim (enforced by scripts/verify-stock.sh). Mark
# them vendored so GitHub's language stats reflect this project's own code
# -- the wasm amalgamation, the WASI shims, the witnesses, the build --
# rather than upstream Lua.
src/**   linguist-vendored
tests/** linguist-vendored

# ...but these are ours, not upstream:
src/onelua.c -linguist-vendored
src/wasi/**  -linguist-vendored
